      <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100">MARC Tools <span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border dark:border-slate-600">BETA</span></h1>
